I have files in my repo whose names begin with a period, e.g. .htaccess and .editorconfig. When I right-click and select Annotate Selected... or Log Selected... from the pop-up menu, I get this error:

{{*Potential security error detected in the specified Url*}}

{{Sourcetree determined this URL is in an unsupported format.}}

 

I get the same error with other file names beginning with a period. The exception is .gitignore files - no error with those. 

{{ }}
